{"id": "xos035", "name": "Audio_CArea_702_11_08_2", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... Hey, where are you taking me?\n"}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Agent N"], "content": "Shut up and just come with me.\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→Signal Switch]</i>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Agent N"], "content": "We're here. Now, stand still.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "Punch"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Ugh!\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Agent N"], "content": "This one is for your father.\nIf he is still alive, I'm certain this is what he will do.\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Agent N"], "content": "Because of my position, I never had the opportunity to talk to you since your arrest, until now\nSpeak. What the hell is all this stuff about? Before Kyle died, he truly believed that his son has changed for good. Is this your response to his expectations? By causing all this nonsensical mess?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... You haven't changed one bit.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Lighting_smoke", "Lights fire"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Agent N"], "content": "...... (Inhales)\nIf it's so easy to change, I would never be able to hold his position to this day.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... Sorry, I didn't mean for things to turn out this way.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Agent N"], "content": "That is not what I want to hear. What happened exactly?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "It's a bit complicated.\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Agent N"], "content": "You have until this cigarette burns out to explain.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... That's more or less it. The real Æsir is definitely still hiding somewhere right now. He is using the window created by all this chaos to carry out his next plan... We have no idea what secrets A.R.C. is hiding either.\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Agent N"], "content": "...... (Exhales)\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Agent N"], "content": "...... Kyle often used to say, \"No matter what kind of justice we uphold,\"...\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "\"we are always the villain in someone else's story.\"\n...... His favorite saying.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Agent N"], "content": "Later, I was able to understand this saying in an even deeper way. This means that every single villain has something they upheld as their justice.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Agent N"], "content": "How should I believe that the story you just told is not a load of crap?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... You don't have to believe. You just have to know, that for the sake of pursuing the truth, I am willing to give up my most treasured things. Even if I become a villain in your eyes, I will not stop.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Agent N"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "If you don't unlock these handcuffs now, this case will never end. By then, it doesn't matter if it's your justice or mine; they will all be reduced to ashes.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Agent N"], "content": "Those eyes... you two are indeed father and son after all.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Button", "Unlocks handcuffs"], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "Punch"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Argh!?\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Agent N"], "content": "The previous punch didn't draw any blood. This one should do. Hey, you punch me a few times too.\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......Huh?\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Agent N"], "content": "Quick.\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "Punch"], "content": ""}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Agent N"], "content": "... Man, do you really eat properly?\nWhatever, just need to cause an injury. This way, I can treat it as if we had a brawl. Oh, and my helmet too. You can break it somehow, right?\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "I can...\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Agent N"], "content": "Go down this door. I will command them to go somewhere else.\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Agent N"], "content": "The justice I... or Kyle upheld may no longer exist anymore. \nHowever, if it's you, maybe there is still hope.\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... Thanks.\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Agent N"], "content": "Oh, one more thing. \"Willing to give up my most treasured things.\" Don't say that until you've lost something for real.\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……おい、どこへ連れて行く気だ。\n"}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "お前は黙って付いて来ればいいんだよ。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→シグナル切り替え]</i>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "着いた。そこに立て。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "殴る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "グハッ！\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "これはお前の親父さんの代わりの一発だ。\nあの人がまだ生きてたら、きっとこうしてただろうからな。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "俺の地位の問題で、お前が捕まってから今まで、お前と話す機会がなかった。\nほら、話せよ。お前何やってんだ？\nKyleさんは死ぬまで自分の息子は変わったって信じてた。\n今、お前がここをこんな滅茶苦茶にしてるって知ったら悲しむと思わないか？\nこれがあの人のお前に対する期待への答えか？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……あんたは変わってないな。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Lighting_smoke", "火をつける"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "……（タバコを吸う）\nそんな簡単に変われたら、あの人の椅子を今まで守ったりできなかったよ。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……こんなことになって、悪かった。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "俺が聞きたいのはそんな言葉じゃない。\n何があったんだ？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "話すと長くなる。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "タバコ1本分の時間をやるよ。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……っていう感じだ。\n本物のÆsirはまだどこかに隠れてる。\nきっとこの混乱したスキを狙って、また何か次の計画を練っているはずだ……\nA.R.C.にもどんな秘密が隠されているのか分からない。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "……（煙を吐く）\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "……Kyleさんがよく言ってたな。\n「どんなに正義を貫こうと、」\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "「誰かの物語の中では必ず悪者になってしまう。」\n……あの人の一番好きな言葉だ。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "年を重ねて、より深くこの言葉の意味がよく分かるようになったよ。\nどんな悪者にも自分の貫くべき正義があるってことだ。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "お前の話が嘘でないと、俺はどうやって信じたらいい？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……信じる必要はない。\n知っていてくれればいい。\n俺は、真実を追い求めるために、何よりも大切な物を捨てる覚悟がある。\nあんたにとって、俺が悪者になったとしても構わない。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "今、この手錠を解かなければ、この件は終わりだ。\n俺にとっての正義も、お前にとっての正義も、何もかも消えてなくなってしまう。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "お前の目……親子だな。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Button", "手錠アンロック"], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………！\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "殴る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "グハッ！\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "さっき殴った時血が出なかっただろ？\nこれでいい。\nおい、お前も俺を1発殴れ。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……は？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "早くしろ。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "殴る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "……おいおい、ちゃんと飯食ってんのか？\nまあいい。傷さえあれば問題ない。\nこれで俺たちは戦ったことになる。\n俺のヘルメット、お前壊せるよな？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "できるけど……\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "この扉から下へ行け。\n他の奴らには違う場所へ行かせる。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "俺や……Kyleさんの貫きたかった正義はとっくに存在しなかったのかもしれない。\nだが、お前にはまだ希望がある。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……ありがとう。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "そうだ。\n「何よりも大切な物を捨てる覚悟がある」なんて言葉は、本当に失ってから使えよな。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……喂，你要把我帶去哪？\n"}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "閉嘴，乖乖跟我走。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "到了，站好。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "拳擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "呃啊！\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "這拳是代替你爸揍的，他如果還活著，就會這麼做。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "因為職位的關係，從你被抓到現在都沒機會跟你說話。\n說吧，你到底在搞什麼飛機？Kyle 死前還一直相信自己的兒子變了，現在這樣把這裡弄得雞飛狗跳就是你對他期待的回應嗎？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……你都沒變啊。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Lighting_smoke", "點火"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "……（吸煙）\n如果那麼容易變就不可能撐著他的位子到現在了。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……抱歉，事情變成這樣。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "我要聽的不是這個，到底發生什麼事了？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "有點複雜。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "給你一支煙的時間。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……事情就是這樣。真正的 Æsir 現在一定也還躲在哪個角落，利用這陣混亂的空檔進行下一個計畫……A.R.C. 也不知道藏著什麼祕密。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "……（吐煙）\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "……以前 Kyle 常說，「無論堅持怎樣的正義」……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "「我們都一定會在某人的故事中扮演反派」……他最喜歡的銘言。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "我後來又更深刻地理解這句話了，這代表每一個反派，都一定有他們自己堅持的正義。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "我要怎樣相信你這段故事不是謊言？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……你不用相信。你只要知道，為了追查真相，我願意捨棄自己最珍貴的東西，就算成為你眼中的惡人也無所謂。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "現在不把這副手銬解開，這件事情就不會結束，無論是我或你堅持的正義到時候都會化為烏有。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "你的眼神……你們果然是父子啊。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Button", "手銬解鎖"], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "拳擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "呃啊！？\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "剛剛揍你沒有流血啊，這樣就行了。喂，你也揍我幾拳。\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……吭？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "快點。\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "拳擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "……你有沒有吃飯啊？\n算了，有傷就好，這樣就當成是我們打過了。還有我的頭盔，你有辦法弄壞對吧？\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "是可以……\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "從這個門下去吧，我會指揮他們去別的地方。\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "我……或是 Kyle 堅持的正義可能早就不存在了，但你的話也許還有希望。\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……謝了。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "對了，「願意捨棄自己最珍貴的東西」這種話，等你真的失去了再說吧。\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "...저기, 절 어디로 데려가는 거죠?\n"}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["집법원 N"], "content": "닥치고 얌전히 따라오기나 해.\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→신호 변경]</i>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["집법원 N"], "content": "도착했다. 똑바로 서.\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": ".......?\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "주먹을 날린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "으윽!\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["집법원 N"], "content": "이건 네 애비 대신 주는 선물이다.\n살아있었다면, 분명 이렇게 했겠지.\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["집법원 N"], "content": "내 계급 때문에 네가 잡힌 이후로 같이 대화할 기회가 없었군.\n말하거라. 대체 뭘 꾸미고 있는 거지? Kyle은 죽기 전에도 끝까지 자기 아들이 변했다고 믿고 있었어. 그런데도 넌 지금 이렇게 도망자 신세가 되어버렸지. 이것이 네가 바라던 아버지 기대에 대한 보답이야?\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "...당신은 하나도 안 변했군요.\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Lighting_smoke", "불을 붙인다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["집법원 N"], "content": "...(담배를 빨아들인다) \n그렇게 쉽게 변할 수 있었다면, 그분의 자리를 지금까지 지켜올 수 없었겠지.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "....죄송합니다. 상황을 이렇게까지 악화시켜서.\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["집법원 N"], "content": "사과 따윌 듣자는 게 아니야.\n대체 무슨 일이 일어났던 거냐?\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "얘기하자면 조금 길어요.\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["집법원 N"], "content": "담배 한 개 피울 동안 얘기해 보라고.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "...그렇게 된 겁니다. 진짜 Æsir은 지금 어딘가에 숨어서 이번 혼란을 틈타 다음 계획을 진행하고 있을 겁니다... A.R.C.가 어떤 비밀을 숨기고 있는지는 저도 잘...\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["집법원 N"], "content": "……(담배 연기를 내뱉는다)\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["집법원 N"], "content": "...예전에 Kyle이 늘 하던 말이 있지.\n「어떤 정의를 추구하든지 간에」……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "「누군가에겐 악역으로 비칠 뿐이다」...아버지가 가장 좋아하던 말이죠.\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["집법원 N"], "content": "시간이 흐르고 나서야 그 말을 더욱 잘 이해하게 됐어. 악역을 맡은 자들 역시 그들만의 정의가 있었다는 의미겠지.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": ".....\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["집법원 N"], "content": "내가 어떻게 해야 네가 한 이야기가 거짓말이 아니란 것을 믿을 수 있지?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "...믿을 필요 없어요. 그저 제가 진실을 좇기 위해 가장 소중한 것을 버릴 각오가 돼있다는 사실만 알아주신다면, 아저씨 눈에 제가 악당으로 비친다 해도 상관없습니다.\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["집법원 N"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "지금 이 수갑을 풀지 않으면, 이 사건은 절대 해결할 수 없을 겁니다. 그렇게 되면 저도 아저씨도, 우리가 추구하던 정의는 결국 아무것도 아니게 돼버릴 거예요.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["집법원 N"], "content": "그 눈...역시 그 애비에 그 자식이군.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Button", "수갑을 풀어준다."], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......!\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "주먹을 날린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "크억!?\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["집법원 N"], "content": "방금 때렸을 때, 피가 안 났잖아. 이럼 됐겠지. 자, 너도 날 몇 대 쳐.\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "...네?\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["집법원 N"], "content": "서둘러!\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "주먹을 날린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["집법원 N"], "content": "......네 녀석, 밥은 제대로 먹고 다니는 거냐?\n뭐, 됐다. 작은 상처라도 입었으면 상관없겠지. 그리고 내 헬멧, 너라면 충분히 고장낼 수 있겠지?\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "가능합니다....\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["집법원 N"], "content": "이 문으로 내려가라. 저 녀석들은 내가 지휘해서 다른 곳으로 보낼 테니.\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["집법원 N"], "content": "나와...그리고 Kyle이 추구했던 정의는 이미 진작에 사라져버렸는지도. 하지만 네 녀석의 정의는 아직 희망이 있을지도 모르지.\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "...고맙습니다.\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["집법원 N"], "content": "아, 그리고\n「가장 소중한 것을 버릴 각오가 돼있다」라는 말은, 네가 진짜로 소중한 것을 잃어버렸을 때나 말하도록 하라고.\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……喂，你要把我帶去哪？\n"}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "閉嘴，乖乖跟我走。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[→切換訊號]</i>\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "到了，站好。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Punch", "拳擊"], "content": ""}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "呃啊！\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "這拳是代替你爸揍的，他如果還活著，就會這麼做。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "因為職位的關係，從你被抓到現在都沒機會跟你說話。\n說吧，你到底在搞什麼飛機？Kyle 死前還一直相信自己的兒子變了，現在這樣把這裡弄得雞飛狗跳就是你對他期待的回應嗎？\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……你都沒變啊。\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Lighting_smoke", "點火"], "content": ""}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "……（吸煙）\n如果那麼容易變就不可能撐著他的位子到現在了。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……抱歉，事情變成這樣。\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "我要聽的不是這個，到底發生什麼事了？\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "有點複雜。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "給你一支煙的時間。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……事情就是這樣。真正的 Æsir 現在一定也還躲在哪個角落，利用這陣混亂的空檔進行下一個計畫……A.R.C. 也不知道藏著什麼祕密。\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "……（吐煙）\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "……以前 Kyle 常說，「無論堅持怎樣的正義」……\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "「我們都一定會在某人的故事中扮演反派」……他最喜歡的銘言。\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "我後來又更深刻地理解這句話了，這代表每一個反派，都一定有他們自己堅持的正義。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "我要怎樣相信你這段故事不是謊言？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……你不用相信。你只要知道，為了追查真相，我願意捨棄自己最珍貴的東西，就算成為你眼中的惡人也無所謂。\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "現在不把這副手銬解開，這件事情就不會結束，無論是我或你堅持的正義到時候都會化為烏有。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["執法員 N"], "content": "你的眼神……你們果然是父子啊。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Button", "手銬解鎖"], "content": ""}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……！\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Pu